$ git init
Initialized empty Git repository in C:/git-handsons/.git/

$ echo "Welcome to the version control" >> welcome.txt

$ ls -al

$ cat welcome.txt
Welcome to the version control

$ git status
On branch master

No commits yet

Untracked files:
